title: Genju of the Fens
text: Enchant Swamp: Until end of turn, enchanted Swamp becomes a 2/2 black Spirit creature with ": This creature gets +1/+1 until end of turn." It's still a land.When enchanted Swamp is put into a graveyard, you may return Genju of the Fens from your graveyard to your hand.
expansion: Duel Decks Anthology, Garruk vs. Liliana
